<FIRST>r w PM-WashingtoninBrief     05-12 0523</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Washington in Brief,520</SECOND>
<HEAD>Yeutter Says Steel Industry Will Benefit from Canada Pact</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
