TION> 737 landed, ambulances and fire trucks waiting. Despite the experience, Ms. <PERSON> Tompkins </PERSON> told the <ORGANIZATION> ALPA </ORGANIZATION> gathering Wednesday that she is ready to get back to the cockpit. `` I ` m looking forward to going back to <LOCATION> Hawaii </LOCATION> and flying again,'' she said.
