<HEAD>Woman Who Escaped 10{ Years Ago Captured in Maryland</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SEVERN, Md. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 A woman who walked away from a <LOCATION> South </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Carolina </LOCATION> prison work-release program 10 -LCB- years ago has been arrested in <LOCATION> Maryland </LOCATION>, where she had become a successful businesswoman, authorities said. <PERSON> Pamela </PERSON> <PERSON> A. </PERSON> <PERSON> Rogers </PERSON>, 36, who served three years of a 12-year sentence for armed robbery, was arrested Tuesday at her home in Severn, where she had lived under a different name with her husband and two sons from an earlier marriage. `` Ten-and-a-half years, 10 -LCB- years, 10 -LCB- years, why now?'' the woman, a successful real estate broker, asked as she was arrested, according to <PERSON> Rodney </PERSON> <PERSON> Johnson </PERSON>, warrants supervisor with the <LOCATION> U.S </LOCATION>. Marshal's Office in <LOCATION> Baltimore </LOCATION>. <PERSON> Johnson </PERSON> said Ms. <PERSON> Rogers </PERSON> had lived in Severn since shortly after the escape and had assumed the name <PERSON> Kay </PERSON> <PERSON> Kathalena </PERSON> <PERSON> Smith </PERSON> and a birthdate five years prior to her real birthdate. She worked as a waitress and about 18 months ago obtained her real estate license. <PERSON> Johnson </PERSON> said the woman had more than $ 1 million in sales last year and apparently lived an honest life since her escape. Ms. <PERSON> Rogers </PERSON>, convicted in the armed robbery of a <LOCATION> Columbia </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> S.C. </LOCATION>, jewelry store, had been wanted since Jan. 7, 1978, when she failed to return to <ORGANIZATION> Goodman </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Correctional </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Institution </ORGANIZATION> near <LOCATION> Columbia </LOCATION> from a work-release job, said state <ORGANIZATION> Department </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Corrections </ORGANIZATION> spokesman <PERSON> Hal </PERSON> <PERSON> Leslie </PERSON>. An old phone number and information provided by her fo