<HEAD>Afghan Rebels Down Soviet Helicopter; Soviet Troops Withdrawing</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Najib is full name</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By MOHAMMED AFTAB</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>ISLAMABAD, Pakistan (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
