</TEXT>
<TEXT>
 Minister of Overseas Territories <PERSON> Olivier </PERSON> <PERSON> Stern </PERSON>, 52, is to the right of the mainstream Socialists and is a former member of the conservative Rally for the Republic. He served as minister of overseas territories from 1974-78 under the <PERSON> Chirac </PERSON> government. <PERSON> Stern </PERSON>'s problems include resolving the political crisis in <LOCATION> France </LOCATION>'s <LOCATION> Pacific </LOCATION> territory of <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Caledonia </LOCATION>
