ld closed in <LOCATION> Hong </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Kong </LOCATION> at $ 450.06, down from $ 451.68. On the Commodity Exchange in <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION>, gold bullion for current delivery rose $ 2.20 a troy ounce to $ 451.90 Silver bullion traded late in <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> at $ 6.56 bid a troy ounce, up from $ 6.55. On the <ORGANIZATION> New </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> York </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Comex </ORGANIZATION>, the price was $ 6.574, up 2.2 cents.
